#. <section class="sutta" id="sn35.81"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.81:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.81:0.2"
msgid "8. Gilānavagga"
msgstr "8. Sick"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 81. Sambahulabhikkhusutta → bhikkhu (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.81:0.3"
msgid "81. Sambahulabhikkhusutta"
msgstr "81. Several Mendicants"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.51"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.81:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu … pe … ekamantaṃ "
"nisinnā kho te bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr "Then several mendicants went up to the Buddha … and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn35.81:1.2"
msgid "“idha no, bhante, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā amhe evaṃ pucchanti:"
msgstr "“Sir, sometimes wanderers who follow other paths ask us:"

msgctxt "sn35.81:1.3"
msgid "‘kimatthiyaṃ, āvuso, samaṇe gotame brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘Reverends, what’s the purpose of living the spiritual life with the ascetic "
"Gotama?’"

msgctxt "sn35.81:1.4"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ puṭṭhā mayaṃ, bhante, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ "
"byākaroma:"
msgstr "We answer them like this:"

msgctxt "sn35.81:1.5"
msgid "‘dukkhassa kho, āvuso, pariññatthaṃ bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The purpose of living the spiritual life under the Buddha is to completely "
"understand suffering.’"

msgctxt "sn35.81:1.6"
msgid ""
"Kacci mayaṃ, bhante, evaṃ puṭṭhā evaṃ byākaramānā vuttavādino ceva bhagavato "
"homa, na ca bhagavantaṃ abhūtena abbhācikkhāma, dhammassa cānudhammaṃ "
"byākaroma, na ca koci sahadhammiko vādānuvādo gārayhaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgacchatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Answering this way, we trust that we repeat what the Buddha has said, and "
"don’t misrepresent him with an untruth. We trust our explanation is in line "
"with the teaching, and that there are no legitimate grounds for rebuke or "
"criticism.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.52"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.81:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Taggha tumhe, bhikkhave, evaṃ puṭṭhā evaṃ byākaramānā vuttavādino ceva me "
"hotha, na ca maṃ abhūtena abbhācikkhatha, dhammassa cānudhammaṃ byākarotha, "
"na ca koci sahadhammiko vādānuvādo gārayhaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgacchati."
msgstr ""
"“Indeed, in answering this way you repeat what I’ve said, and don’t "
"misrepresent me with an untruth. Your explanation is in line with the "
"teaching, and there are no legitimate grounds for rebuke or criticism."

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.2"
msgid "Dukkhassa hi, bhikkhave, pariññatthaṃ mayi brahmacariyaṃ vussati."
msgstr ""
"For the purpose of living the spiritual life under me is to completely "
"understand suffering."

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.3"
msgid "Sace pana vo, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "If wanderers who follow other paths were to ask you:"

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.4"
msgid ""
"‘katamaṃ pana taṃ, āvuso, dukkhaṃ, yassa pariññāya samaṇe gotame "
"brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti?"
msgstr "‘Reverends, what is that suffering?’"

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ "
"byākareyyātha:"
msgstr "You should answer them:"

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.6"
msgid ""
"‘cakkhu kho, āvuso, dukkhaṃ, tassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussati."
msgstr ""
"‘Reverends, the eye is suffering. The purpose of living the spiritual life "
"under the Buddha is to completely understand this."

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.7"
msgid "Rūpā … pe …"
msgstr "Sights … Eye consciousness … Eye contact …"

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.8"
msgid ""
"yampidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā "
"adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi dukkhaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by eye "
"contact is also suffering."

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.9"
msgid "Tassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussati … pe …"
msgstr ""
"The purpose of living the spiritual life under the Buddha is to completely "
"understand this."

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.10"
msgid "mano dukkho … pe …"
msgstr "Ear … Nose … Tongue … Body … Mind …"

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.11"
msgid ""
"yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā "
"adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi dukkhaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by mind "
"contact is also suffering."

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.12"
msgid "Tassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussati."
msgstr ""
"The purpose of living the spiritual life under the Buddha is to completely "
"understand this."

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.13"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ kho taṃ, āvuso, dukkhaṃ, tassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ "
"vussatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"This is that suffering. The purpose of living the spiritual life under the "
"Buddha is to completely understand this.’"

msgctxt "sn35.81:2.14"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ "
"byākareyyāthā”ti."
msgstr ""
"When questioned by wanderers who follow other paths, that’s how you should "
"answer them.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.81:2.15"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
